Package: mDLNM
Type: Package
Title: Meta Package for Multiple Exposure Distributed Lag Non-linear Models (DLNM)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Tianyi", "Pan",
      email = "tianyi.pan@uwaterloo.ca",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: A meta-package that supports: (1) Single-index adaptive cumulative exposure DLNM, 
  (2) Additive adaptive cumulative exposure DLNM,
  (3) Single-index distributed response function DLNM, and 
  (4) Additive distributed response function DLNM. 
